returns.delegateAllocations: The amount to send to delegates instead of adding to the local balance.
returns.memo: the memo to override the pay(..) memo
returns.weight: the weight to use to override the funding cycle weight

params.data: the data passed to the data source in terminal.redeemTokensOf(..), as a JBRedeemParamsData struct:

returns.delegateAllocations: The amount to send to delegates instead of adding to the beneficiary.
returns.memo: The memo to override the redeemTokensOf(..) memo.
returns.reclaimAmount: The amount to claim, overriding the terminal logic.

@title Datasource
